title: Watch Blue Origin launch 1st wheelchair user to space on Dec. 18
description: Aerospace engineer Michi Benthaus will become the first wheelchair user ever to reach space on Thursday (Dec. 18), and you can watch her historic launch atop a Blue Origin rocket live.
